    *   `findIdx (fun x => decide (x > i)) ...` finds the first index `j` such that the sum of lengths up to `j` (i.e., `(map length L).partialSums[j]`) is greater than `i`. This corresponds to the sublist `L[j]` containing the `i`-th element of `L.flatten`.
